/*********************	Abstract	*********************************/

	FunLife was created by Ryan Chou (ryanchou0210@gmail.com) in 2013 
	It is an Android App and developed in Android Studio. 


/*********************	Feature		**********************************/
	Its major feature is to find the famous scenary nearby/in specified area.
	In addition, it might combine the user data retrieved from Facebook. 
	Provided FB data, it could provides scenary user may be interested.

																		
/********************	Language	*********************************/
	Sor far FunLife only support the languages listed below:
 		a. English
 		b. Tranditional-Chineise
 	
